{"tid":20591,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真]曼城傻仔來","createTime":"2016-12-03T12:31:55.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T14:26:09.000Z","uid":33808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d0b138a35469f0631e8ebe0e47e8fada6795996c","tid":20591,"uid":33808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T12:31:55.000Z","msg":"同車仔鬥玩三後衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地甘地玩慣<br />\n兩閘助攻助守<br />\n近排適應曬無敵咁濟<br />\n你曼城後方本身已經唔穩<br />\n而家仲要玩花式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前線人多有撚用<br />\n又咪係猜唔入齋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認真有冇人解得通哥狗思路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就覺得真係癡撚線<br />\n自己拎來衰，而且係超樣衰大敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:真係買咗車仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c18275214f17d25bf8e7e4420b58e034672e2d","tid":20591,"uid":33808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T12:33:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec438ac14b4e147cc5c1fb90d133b289ea8daf00","tid":20591,"uid":33808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T12:33:58.000Z","msg":"鏝狗不願面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f62dbbc790ae85dd05a40a82552b7b60b568b5dc","tid":20591,"uid":33808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T12:36:34.000Z","msg":"鏝狗留曬係高登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fbfbd5766a1a7f4161d8a42cb0113d0f79e7c9b","tid":20591,"uid":33808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T12:40:06.000Z","msg":"鏝城球迷走光了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fff560efc33b7f8f90afc9fb980c3da469e22ed","tid":20591,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T12:41:28.000Z","msg":"Stones <img src=\"